variables
	All variables are constants in puppet

	qualified variable names
		allows variables to be accessed when out of scope

		::toplevelvar

		class::var-name

scope
	provides a sandbox within which variables are accessible

	variables may only be accessed from a given scope if declared in it's parent scope or the current one, or if referenced using a qualified name


	top-level scope

		node-scope

			class-scope

				child-class-scope